What:		/sys/bus/i2c/devices/[0-9]+-0078/fuse/status
Date:		June 2024
KernelVersion:	6.6
Contact:	"Jim Wylder" <jwylder@google.com>
Description:
	Show status of the fuse. 'open' = 1 water has been detected at some point
	while the fuse was enabled. 'short' = 0 water has not been detected
	with the fuse enabled.

What:		/sys/bus/i2c/devices/[0-9]+-0078/reference/realtime_value
Date:		June 2024
KernelVersion:	6.6
Contact:	"Jim Wylder" <jwylder@google.com>
Description:
	Diagnostic sensor reading to determine proper functioning of sensor.
	Shows values in realtime.  Return values are:
	0 for short connection,
	1 for open connection.

